channel.title: Tskill is not recognized
channel.description:
Im trying to make an endserver.bat that closes out my runserver.bat and then closes itself. I see a lot of tutorials saying tskill java /a and stuff but i put that in notepad and save as endserver.bat and put in my server folder and all it does is open for a split second and then close out. So I used my hypercam to film it and it said..
"tskill" is not recognized as an internal or external command.
How do I make this work and/or how do I make an endserver.bat that works?
